OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHouseholds to receive      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fenergy payment from January
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Households in Northern Ireland will    
OL,6, receive a single payment of #600       
OL,7, starting in January to help with their 
OL,8, energy bills.                          
OL,10,FThe UK government confirmed electricity
OL,11,Ffirms will be funded for the payments, 
OL,12,Fwith direct debit customers receiving  
OL,13,Fthe money into their bank accounts.    
OL,15,FOther customers will be sent a voucher 
OL,16,Fto redeem the payment.                 
OL,18,FThe money is intended to help with     
OL,19,Fenergy bills but people can use the    
OL,20,Fcash payment as they see fit.          
